---
layout: null
---
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<rss version="2.0">
  <channel>
    <title>날마다 소품</title>
    <description>정성스럽게 지은 패브릭 소품 제작 과정과 따뜻한 일상 이야기를 나눕니다.</description>
    <link>https://nalmadasopum.com</link>
    {% for post in site.posts limit:20 %}
      <item>
        <title>{{ post.title | xml_escape }}</title>
        <description>{{ post.excerpt | strip_html | xml_escape }}</description>
        <pubDate>{{ post.date | date_to_rfc822 }}</pubDate>
        <link>https://nalmadasopum.com{{ post.url }}</link>
        <guid isPermaLink="true">https://nalmadasopum.com{{ post.url }}</guid>
      </item>
    {% endfor %}
  </channel>
</rss>